✨Meet our newest 8zer✨

We’re excited to welcome Bridget Hillard to our Boulder County Team.

As a teacher turned real estate agent, Bridget brings over 20 years of experience helping people navigate pivotal life decisions with clarity and confidence. She has a deep understanding of human connection with expert negotiation skills, honed through her graduate school experience at the Humphrey School of Public Affairs.
And as a native Midwesterner, Bridget has cultivated a nationwide network of real estate professionals. In her free time, Bridget enjoys reading (she belongs to three book clubs), creating art and writing poetry, and exploring new places with her family.
